verbose_text: Further investigation indicated that DCUN1D1 overexpression restored the suppressive effects of miR-195 on the proliferation, migration and invasion of cervical cancer cells, deonstrating that DCUN1D1 functions as a downstream effecter of miR-195 in cervical cancer cells.
evidence: DCUN1D1 overexpression restored the suppressive effects of miR-195 on the proliferation, migration and invasion
